Text.string: Holder, Holder! Ahhhh. Yes, buddy, we're on the blood path now. Holder! Holder? Where are you, Holder?
Name's Ramsden, First Knuckle of the Fingerbite gang. My right-hand man, Holder—well, the Shanks have him now. There's a key around here somewhere. The key to Shankland. To Holder.
Me and Holder, we have to talk. Face to face. Otherwise, the Fingerbites and the Shanks are on the blood path.
Wake him up. Gotta make sure it's Holder. I must speak to Holder. Face to face.
Not him. I know every scar on Holder's body. Tricky bastards, these Shanks. Look around.
Knew it. That must lead to Holder. Well done! I'll get the gang together. A welcome party.||[singing] We're on the blood path now, my buddy!
The Shanks don't deserve Holder. He's one of the best. We were gonna own this whole joint someday.
Who sent you? This is Shankland! Get off our turf.
Enough! Stop shooting, you maniac! You're a killer, I get it! Y'know... the Shanks could use someone like you. Come here.
Who the hell are you?
You Holder? Ramsden sent me to rescue you.
Are you Holder? Ramsden sent me to free you.
Is your name Holder? Ramsden sent me to find you.
Ramsden sent me for you, Holder. So, you're welcome.
Ramsden? You're working for “No Fingers” Ramsden, as in, “he eats his enemies' fingers for freaking fun”? The Shanks have been hiding me from that animal, and now you've led him right to me!
Lots of bodies. Looks like they were tortured.
Phhf. Loads of dead bodies, man. What's going on?
There are many dead and mangled human frames here. And ample blood.
Lotta dead bodies, boyo—d'ya host a potluck or something?
I'm a dead man. I'm a dead man! Better kiss my fingers goodbye! Unless... yeah, yeah. You're a killer, right? Keep that guy away from my fingers and I'll make it worth your while.
Knocky-knock... let me in, Vault Hunter. Holder stole my favorite gun and left the Biters. I need to speak with my good buddy and set things straight.
Don't do it! He's a monster! He'll stab you in the back! Protect me, and... and I'll give you my personal shield!
Stay away from me, you crazy bastard!
Holder, buddy, pal. It's time we had a face-to-face...
Stay on your turf, Ramsden. You stay on your turf, and I'll stay on mine.
Nah, buddy. That's not how it works.||[singing] We're on the blood path now, oh yeah! We're on the blood path now.
I like my fingers!
I'm sure you do, buddy. Thing is, I like 'em too! Hahaha!
We're on the blood path now!
We're on the blood path now!
We're on the blood path now!
We're on the blood path—now!
Welcome to Shankland! Kill 'em all!
[anguished cries]
I am a dead man!
He's gonna kill me!
I'm dead. I'm a goner!
Yes, all right. We can do this. Get ready.
Yeah, we'll fight off that maniac together!
Well, all right. I'm coming for you, Holder, buddy. Me and the gang! Kill. Holder.
We're on the blood path now, you and I...
So long, Holder. See, that's what you get when you betray your friends. If you're born a Fingerbiter, you die a Fingerbiter.
All yours. Now if you'll excuse me, I gotta be alone with my buddy. Say my... last goodbye.
Intruders!
Now get the hell out of Shankland. We've gotta rebuild, in case the Biters come to avenge Ramsden.
You gotta help me!
Keep searching. The key's somewhere.
Lousy Shanks. They stole Holder from me.
Now where did I put that key?
You went up against “No Fingers” Ramsden and lived. I can respect that. Here's my shield, as promised.
Defend Shankland!
Juuuust open the door, and I'll chew that gun from his hot tasty fingers and give it to you.
Holder! Get over here, Holder!
Live a Fingerbiter, die a Fingerbiter!
I'm on the blood path now!
Holder! Let me at those fingertips. Holder!
You're gonna die, Holder!
Holder... ugh, Hol-Hol-Holder...
Come on, Shanks! Let's take those Fingerbiters out!
Die, you Fingerbiting bastards!
You're not gonna take me, Ramsden! You sick bastard!
Kill those Fingerbiters!
Defend me!
Damn you... Ramsden...
The key, yes, you found the key. Pick it up. Don't mind the blood. Blood is life, you know?
Agh, this limp... damn Shanks. But you, you're strong. You clear the way, yeah? Go to the gate. Find Holder.
Me and Holder, we were partners. Best buddies. Then the Shanks took him. Second biggest gang in this joint. Once a Shank, die a Shank. That's what they say. We'll make it happen.
Find Holder's cell. It's gotta be close.||[singing] We're on the blood path now!
Wow, you're tough. Sprinkle nails in your ice cream tough. After this is over, I might have a position for you. Depends on what happens to Holder.
